verbose_text: Therefore, it is possible that E - / B 48 lipoproteins interact with cell membrane receptors, such as LRP-5 through unknown mechanisms, and may activate cytosolic ATM; activated ATM in turn activates class III PI3K, regulating the endocytosis of E - / B 48 lipoproteins.
